{"tid":1767572,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【取代各區核突斂財燈飾 】文宣燈飾有無得諗？","createTime":"2019-12-03T11:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T12:47:05.000Z","uid":221265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c4f0959b2b9f6bd8713877595b5791087de6bc","tid":1767572,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkE6kPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkE6kPL.jpg&h=af16ac7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3rMkPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3rMkPM.jpg&h=a40d4544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCMkqgr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCMkqgr.jpg&h=19d62f4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有巴打話不如諗下文宣燈飾，我唔知區會農曆年嘅燈飾/裝飾批咗未<br />\n(元朗區好似話批咗138萬！)<br />\n如果可推倒重來(新一屆一月返工)，可否攪下文宣燈飾？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議會批120萬整bad taste聖誕燈飾  淘寶：1萬人仔ok<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aoFRcfU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aoFRcfU</a><br />\n<br />\n881晴朗訪候任元朗區議員 講112萬核突燈飾 原來仲有138萬農曆燈飾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eCtKtS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eCtKtS</a><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣1.4億起社區會堂只用250人 平均每個位造價係2020東京奧運新國立競技場3倍幾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eCvBjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eCvBjS</a><br />\n<br />\n【撥亂反正●元朗】33民主派連任候任區議員去信路政署 促擱置審批17億天價橋標書<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1763199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1763199</a>"},{"pid":"1c3e0c6eccfbb07f50e6036ba1c27124fc7ef686","tid":1767572,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:42:55.000Z","msg":"天氣開始轉涼啦～ 冬至好快就到~ 大家諗起啲咩呢？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767560</a>"}